    <div class="main review-item" id="1430189">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1430189/" class="title-link">“东写西读”之《十宅论》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1430189"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1086544/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1086544-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1086544/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">赛宁</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-07-06"
      class="main-meta">2008-07-06 10:55:49</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1430189_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  日本话里有个成语，叫“十人十色”，翻译过来，就是十个人有十种性格的意思，归纳起来讲，就是性格各异。而本书的副标题，大约也就是从这个成语中化来的，叫做“十种人的十种居住方式”，所以，书名就叫做《十宅论》了，听起来很有点日本味，因为，这本书本来就是日本人写的，...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">7有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1430189_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1430189_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



