  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1421781">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1421781/" class="title-link">十个阶层 十种住宅</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1421781"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/myidear/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1044465-22.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/myidear/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">myidear</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-06-27"
      class="main-meta">2008-06-27 14:26:36</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1421781_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  日本有10个阶层，各个阶层都有自己固定的住宅风格。  1986年，31岁（还没有自己的建筑师事务所）的隈研吾在纽约对日本人和住宅做出了上述判断。在《十宅论》中，作者生搬硬套的“捏造”了十类日本人及其住宅，也就是单身公寓派、清里食宿公寓派、咖啡吧派、哈比达派、建筑师派...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1421781/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">11有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1421781_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1421781_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
